ygData.messageBody:
Anyone know how many sailing routes in EQ?

There is a boat from BB, and in between the way to FP, there are 3-4 stops
I guess. Anyone know what places are those stops?

Is there any sea transport from erudin to freeport? If yes, is the erudin
port far (dangerous?) from the erudin city? Thx.

Lastly, other than boat, spells, is there any other means to travel between
different continents (eg natural portal like UO moongate, air ship etc) ?
Mondain
